   857Рєњ#### `P._` wildcard
   859РєњThe `P._` pattern will match any value. You can also use `P.any`, which is an alias to `P._`.
   860Рєњ
   861Рєњ```ts
   862Рєњimport { match, P } from 'ts-pattern';
   863Рєњ
   864Рєњconst input = 'hello';
   865Рєњ
